# Note: The above entities create a network graph with hubs, high-degree nodes, central nodes, connectors, intermediaries, multiplex, and super nodes, all linked via their respective properties, following the schema. All nodes are connected via properties like `elementManagedBy`, `structuralObservableOf`, `locatedAtLocus`, etc., ensuring no isolated nodes.